quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  21,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  21,1,"qareeb aa gaya hai logon ke hisaab ka waqt, aur woh hain ke ghaflat mein mun moray hue hain"
  21,2,un ke paas jo taaza nasiyaat bhi un ke rab ki taraf se aati hai uss ko bah takalouf suntay hain aur khail mein parre rehtay hain
  21,3,"dil un ke ( doosri hi fikron mein ) munhamik hain aur zalim aapas mein sargoshian karte hain ke"" yeh shakhs aakhir tum jaissa aik bashar hi to hai, phir kya tum aankhon dekhte jadu ke phandey mein phas jao ge? """
  21,4,"Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ne kaha mera rab har uss baat ko jaanta hai jo aasman aur zameen mein ki jaye, woh Sami aur Aleem hai"
  21,5,"woh kehte hain"" balkay yeh paragandah khawab hain, balkay yeh iss ki mann gharat hai, balkay yeh shakhs shayar hai warna yeh laaye koi nishani jis terhan puranay zamane ke rasool nishanion ke sath beje gay thay """
  21,6,"halan ke inn se pehlay koi bastii bhi, jisay hum ne halaak kya, imaan nah layi, ab kya yeh imaan layein ge ?"
  21,7,"aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum se pehlay bhi hum ne insanon hi ko rasool bana kar bheja tha jin par hum wahi kya karte thay tum log agar ilm nahi rakhtay to ehley kitaab se pooch lau"
  21,8,"unn Rasolo-n ko hum ne koi aisa jism nahi diya tha ke woh khatay nah hon, aur nah woh sada jeeney walay thay"
  21,9,"phir dekh lau ke aakhir kaar hum ne un ke sath apne waday poooray kiye, aur inhen aur jis jis ko hum ne chaha bacha liya, aur hadd se guzar jaane walon ko halaak kar diya"
  21,10,"logo, hum ne tumhari taraf aik aisi kitaab bhaije hai jis mein tumhara hi zikar hai, kya tum samajte nahi ho ?"
  21,11,kitni hi zalim bastiyan hain jin ko hum ne pees kar rakh diya aur unn ke baad doosri kisi qoum ko uthaya
  21,12,jab unn ko hamara azaab mahsoos howa to lagey wahan se bhagnay
  21,13,"( kaha gaya )"" bhago nahi, jao apne unhi gharon mein aur aish ke samanon mein jin ke andar tum chain kar rahay thay, shayad ke tum se poocha jaye """
  21,14,"kehnay lagey"" haae hamari kam bakhti, be shak hum khata waar thay """
  21,15,"aur woh yahi pukarte rahay yahan taq ke hum ne un ko khalyaan kar diya, zindagi ka aik sharara taq un mein nah raha"
  21,16,hum ne iss aasman aur zameen ko aur jo kuch bhi un mein hai kuch khail ke tor par nahi banaya hai
  21,17,agar hum koi khilona banana chahtay aur bas yahi kuch hamein karna hota to apne hi paas se kar letay
  21,18,magar hum to baatil par haq ki chout lagatay hain jo is ka sir toar deti hai aur woh dekhte dekhte mِt jata hai aur tumahray liye tabahi hai unn baton ki wajah se jo tum banatay ho
  21,19,zameen aur aasman mein jo makhlooq bhi hai Allah ki hai aur jo ( farishtay ) is ke paas hain woh nah apne aap ko bara samajh kar uss ki bandagi se sartabi karte hain aur nah malool hotay hain
  21,20,"shab o roz is ki tasbeeh karte rehtay hain, Dam nahi letay"
  21,21,kya inn logon ke banaye hue arzi khuda aisay hain ke ( be jaan ko jaan bakhash kar ) uttha khara karte hon ?
  21,22,agar aasman o zameen mein aik Allah ke siwa doosray khuda bhi hotay to ( zameen aur aasman ) dono ka nizaam baggar jata pas pak hai Allah Rab ul Arsh unn baton se jo yeh log bana rahay hain
  21,23,woh apne kamon ke liye ( kisi ke agay ) jawab da nahi hai aur sab jawab da hain
  21,24,"kya ussay chore kar unhon ne dosray khuda bana liye hain? ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho ke"" lao apni Daleel , yeh kitaab bhi mojood hai jis mein mere doori ke logon ke liye nasiyaat hai aur woh kitaaben bhi mojood hain jin mein mujh se pehlay logon ke liye nasiyaat thi"" magar un mein se aksar log haqeeqat se be khabar hain, is liye mun moray hue hain"
  21,25,"hum ne tum se pehlay jo rasool bhi bheja hai uss ko yahi wahi ki hai ke mere siwa koi khuda nahi hai, pas tum log meri hi bandagi karo"
  21,26,"yeh kehte hain"" Rehman aulaad rakhta hai"" subhan Allah , woh to bande hain jinhein azzt di gayi hai"
  21,27,uss ke huzoor barh kar nahi boltay aur bas uss ke hukum par amal karte hain
  21,28,"jo kuch unn ke samnay hai usay bhi woh jaanta hai aur jo kuch unn se oojhal hai is se bhi woh bakhabar hai woh kisi ki sifarish nahi karte bajuz uss ke jis ke haq mein sifarish suneney par Allah raazi ho, aur woh is ke khauf se daray rehtay hain"
  21,29,"aur jo unn mein se koi keh day ke Allah ke siwa mein bhi aik khuda hon, to usay hum Jahannum ki saza den, hamaray haan zaalmon ka yahi badla hai"
  21,30,"kya woh log jinhon ne ( NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki baat maan-ne se ) inkaar kar diya hai ghhor nahi karte ke yeh sab aasman aur zameen baahum miley hue thay, phir hum ne aِnhin judda kya, aur pani se har zindah cheez peda ki kya woh ( hamari is khalaqi ko ) nahi mantay ?"
  21,31,"aur hum ne zameen mein pahar jama diye taakay woh inhen le kar dhalak nah jaye aur is mein kushadah rahein bana den, shayad ke log apna rasta maloom kar len"
  21,32,"aur hum ne aasman ko aik mehfooz chhat bana diya, magar yeh hain ke is ki nishanion ki taraf tojj_h hi nahi karte"
  21,33,aur woh Allah hi hai jis ne raat aur din banaye aur sooraj aur chaand ko peda kya sab aik aik fallak mein teer rahay hain
  21,34,"aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hameshgi to hum ne tum se pehlay bhi kisi ensaan ke liye nahi rakhi hai agar tum mar gay to kya yeh log hamesha jeetay rahen ge ?"
  21,35,"har jandaar ko mout ka maza chakhna hai, aur hum achay aur buray halaat mein daal kar tum sab ki azmaish kar rahay hain aakhir kaar tumhe hamari hi taraf palatna hai"
  21,36,"yeh munkareen haq jab tumhe dekhte hain to tumhara mazaq bana letay hain kehte hain"" kya yeh hai woh shakhs jo tumahray khudaon ka zikar kya karta hai ?"" aur un ka apna haal yeh hai ke Rehman ke zikar se munkir hain"
  21,37,"ensaan jald baz makhlooq hai abhi mein tum ko apni nishanain dukhaay deta hon, jaldi nah macha-o"
  21,38,"yeh log kehte hain"" aakhir yeh dhamki poori kab ho gi agar tum sachey ho """
  21,39,"kash inn kafiroon ko uss waqt ka kuch ilm hota jabkay yeh nah apne mun aag se bacha saken ge nah apnipithain, aur nah un ko kahin se madad puhanche gi"
  21,40,woh bulaa achanak aeye gi aur aِnhin iss terhan yak lakht daboch le gi ke yeh nah is ko dafaa kar saken ge aur nah inn ko lamha bhar mohlat hi mil sakay gi
  21,41,"mazaq tum se pehlay bhi Rasolo-n ka uraya ja chuka hai, magar unn ka mazaq urane walay usi cheez ke phair mein aa kar rahay jis ka woh mazaq uratay thay"
  21,42,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se kaho,"" kon hai jo raat ko ya din ko tumhe Rehman se bacha sakta ho ?"" magar yeh apne rab ki nasiyaat se mun mourr rahay hain"
  21,43,kya yeh kuch aisay khuda rakhtay hain jo hamaray muqablay mein un ki himayat karen? woh nah to khud apni madad kar satke hain aur nah hamari hi taied unn ko haasil hai
  21,44,asal baat yeh hai ke inn logon ko aur inn ke aaba o ajdaad ko hum zindagi ka sir o samaan diye chalay gay yahan taq ke inn ko din lag gay magar kya aِnhin nazar nahi aata ke hum zameen ko mukhtalif simtao se ghta-tay chalay aa rahay hain? phir kya yeh ghalib aa jayen ge ?
  21,45,"inn se keh do ke"" mein to wahi ki bana par tumhe mutnabba kar raha hon"" magar behray pukaar ko nahi suna karte jabkay unhen khabardaar kya jaye"
  21,46,"aur agar tairay rab ka azaab zara sa inhen chhoo jaye to abhi cheekh utheen ke haae hamari kam bakhti, be shak hum khata waar thay"
  21,47,"qayamat ke roz hum theek theek tolnay walay traazo rakh den ge, phir kisi shakhs par zarra barabar zulm nah ho ga jis ka rai ke danay ke barabar bhi kuch kya dhara ho ga woh hum samnay le ayen ge aur hisaab laganay ke liye hum kaafi hain"
  21,48,"pehlay hum moose aur haroon ko Farqan aur roshni aur"" zikar"" ataa kar chuke hain unn mut-taqi logon ki BHALAI ke liye"
  21,49,jo be dekhe apne rab se dareen aur jin ko ( hisaab ki ) uss gharri ka khatka laga howa hai
  21,50,"aur ab yeh babarkat"" zikar"" hum ne ( tumahray liye ) nazil kya hai phir kya tum iss ko qubool karne se inkari ho ?"
  21,51,uss se bhi pehlay hum ne ibrahim ko uss ki hosh mandi bakhsh thi aur hum uss ko khoob jantay thay
  21,52,"yaad karo woh mauqa jabkay uss ne apne baap aur apni qoum se kaha tha ke"" yeh moorten kaisi hain jin ke tum log garweedah ho rahay ho? """
  21,53,"unhon ne jawab diya"" hum ne apne baap dada ko un ki ibadat karte paaya hai """
  21,54,"is ne kaha"" tum bhi gumraah ho aur tumahray baap dada bhi Sarih gumraahi mein parre hue thay? """
  21,55,"unhon ne kaha"" kya to hamaray samnay apne asli khayalat paish kar raha hai ya mazaq karta hai? """
  21,56,"uss ne jawab diya"" nahi, balkay fi al waqea tumhara rab wohi hai jo zameen aur asmano ka rab aur unn ka peda karne wala hai iss par mein tumahray samnay gawahi deta hon"
  21,57,"aur khuda ki qasam mein tumhari ghair mojoodgi mein zaroor tumahray buton ki khabar lon ga """
  21,58,chunancha is ne unn ko tukre tukre kar diya aur sirf un ke barray ko chore diya taakay shayad woh is ki taraf rujoo karen
  21,59,"( onhon ne aa kar buton ka yeh haal dekha to ) kehnay lagey"" hamaray khudaon ka yeh haal kis ne kar diya? bara hi koi zalim tha woh """
  21,60,"( baaz log ) bolay"" hum ne aik nojawan ko un ka zikar karte suna tha jis ka naam ibrahim hai """
  21,61,"unhon ne kaha"" to pakar lao ussay sab ke samnay taakay log dekh len ( uss ki kaisi khabar li jati hai ) """
  21,62,"( ibrahim ke anay par ) onhon ne poocha"" kyun ibrahim, to ne hamaray khudaon ke sath yeh harkat ki hai? """
  21,63,"uss ne jawab diya"" balkay yeh sab kuch un ke is sardar ne kya hai, inn hi se pooch lau agar yeh boltay hon """
  21,64,"yeh sun kar woh log apne zameer ki taraf palty aur ( apne dilon mein ) kehnay lagey"" waqai tum khud hi zalim ho """
  21,65,"magar phir unn ki mat palat gayi aur bolay"" too jaanta hai ke yeh boltay nahi hain """
  21,66,"ibrahim ne kaha"" phir kya tum Allah ko chore kar unn cheezon ko pooj rahay ho jo nah tumhe naffa pohanchanay par Qadir hain nah nuqsaan"
  21,67,"taf hai tum par aur tumahray inn mabodon par jin ki tum Allah ko chore kar pooja kar rahay ho kya tum kuch bhi aqal nahi rakhtay? """
  21,68,"unhon ne kaha"" jala daalo is ko aur himayat karo apne khudaon ki agar tumhe kuch karna hai """
  21,69,"hum ne kaha"" ae aag, thandhi ho ja aur salamti ban ja ibrahim par """
  21,70,woh chahtay thay ke ibrahim ke sath buraii karen magar hum ne un ko burii terhan nakaam kar diya
  21,71,aur hum ne ussay aur loot ko bacha kar uss sarzamen ki taraf le gay jis mein hum ne duniya walon ke liye barkaten rakhi hain
  21,72,"aur hum ne usay ishaq ataa kya aur yaqoob is par mazeed, aur har aik ko Saleh banaya"
  21,73,"aur hum ne unn ko imam bana diya jo hamaray hukum se rahnumai karte thay aur hum ne inhen wahi ke zareya naik kamon ki aur namaz qaim karne aur zkoh dainay ki hadaayat ki, aur woh hamaray ibadat guzaar thay"
  21,74,"aur loot ko hum ne hukum aur ilm bakhsha aur ussay uss bastii se bacha kar nikaal diya jobad karyan karti thi dar haqeeqat woh barri hi burii, fasik qoum thi"
  21,75,"aur loot ko hum ne apni rehmat mein daakhil kya, woh Saleh logon mein se tha"
  21,76,aur yahi Nemat hum ne Nooh ko di yaad karo jabkay inn sab se pehlay uss ne hamein puraka tha hum ne is ki dua qubool ki aur usay aur is ke ghar walon ko karb azeem se nijaat di
  21,77,"aur uss qoum ke muqablay mein uss ki madad ki jis ne hamari ayaat ko jhutla diya tha woh barray buray log thay, pas hum ne un sab ko ghark kar diya"
  21,78,"aur isi Nemat se hum ne Dawood اaur Sulayman ko Sarfraz kya yaad karo woh mauqa jabkay woh dono aik khait ke muqadmay mein faisla kar rahay thay jis mein raat ke waqt doosray logon ki bakriyan phail gayi theen, aur hum unn ki adalat khud dekh rahay thay"
  21,79,"uss waqt hum ne sahih faisla sulaiman ko samgha diya, halaank hukum aur ilm hum ne dono hi ko ataa kya tha Dawood ke sath hum ne pahoron aur parindon ko maskhar kar diya tha jo tasbeeh karte thay, iss feal ke karne walay hum hi thay"
  21,80,"aur hum ne uss ko tumahray faiday ke liye zarah bananay ki sanat sikha di thi, taakay tum ko aik doosray ki maar se bachaaye, phir kya tum shukar guzaar ho ?"
  21,81,"aur sulaiman ke liye hum ne taiz howa ko maskhar kar diya tha jo is ke hukum se uss sarzamen ki taraf chalti thi jis mein hum ne barkaten rakhi hain, hum har cheez ka ilm rakhnay walay thay"
  21,82,aur shyatin mein se hum ne aisay bohat soon ko is ka tabay bana diya tha jo is ke liye ghote lagatay aur is ke siwa doosray kaam karte thay un sab ke nigran hum hi thay
  21,83,"aur yahi ( hosh mandi aur hukum o ilm ki Nemat ) hum ne ayub ko di thi yaad karo, jabkay is ne apne rab ko puraka ke"" mujhe bemari lag gayi hai aur to Arhamhai """
  21,84,"hum ne is ki dua qubool ki aur jo takleef ussay thi is ko door kar diya, aur sirf is ke ahal o Ayal hi is ko nahi diye balkay un ke sath itnay hi aur bhi diye, apni khaas rehmat ke tor par, aur is liye ke yeh aik sabaq ho ibadat guzaron ke liye"
  21,85,aur yahi Nemat Ismael aur Adrees aur ZULKAFFAL ko di ke yeh sab sabir log thay
  21,86,aur un ko hum ne apni rehmat mein daakhil kya ke woh salhoon mein se thay
  21,87,"aur machhli walay ko bhi hum ne nawaza yaad karo jabkay woh baggar kar chala gaya tha aur samgha tha ke hum is par girift nah karen ge aakhir ko uss ne tarikeon mein puraka"" nahi hai koi khuda magar too, pak hai teri zaat, be shak mein ne qasoor kya """
  21,88,"tab hum ne is ki dua qubool ki aur gham se is ko nijaat bakhsh, aur isi terhan hum mominon ko bacha liya karte hain"
  21,89,"aur Zikria ko, jabkay is ne apne rab ko puraka ke"" ae parvar-digaar, mujhe akela nah chore, aur behtareen waris to too hi hai """
  21,90,"pas hum ne is ki dua qubool ki aur usay yahya ataa kya aur is ki biwi ko is ke liye durust kar diya yeh log neki ke kamon mein daud dhoop karte thay aur hamein raghbat aur khauf ke sath pukarte thay, aur hamaray agay jhuke hue thay"
  21,91,aur woh khatoon jis ne apni asmat ki hifazat ki thi hum ne uss ke andar apni rooh se phonka aur ussay aur uss ke betay ko duniya bhar ke liye nishani bana diya
  21,92,"yeh tumhari ammt haqeeqat mein aik hi ammt hai aur mein tumhara rab hon, pas tum meri ibadat karo"
  21,93,magar ( yeh logon ki karstani hai ke ) unhon ne aapas mein deen ko tukre tukre kar dala sab ko hamari taraf palatna hai
  21,94,"phir jo naik amal kere ga, iss haal mein ke woh momin ho, to is ke kaam ki na qadri nah ho gi, aur ussay hum likh rahay hain"
  21,95,aur mumkin nahi hai ke jis bastii ko hum ne halaak kar diya ho woh phir palat sakay
  21,96,yahan taq ke jab Yajooj o majooj khol diye jayen ge aur har bulandi se woh nikal parrin ge
  21,97,"aur wada barhaq ke poora honay ka waqt qareeb aa lagey ga to yaka yak unn logon ke daiday phatay ke phatay reh jayen ge jinhon ne kufar kya tha kahin ge"" haae hamari kam bakhti, hum iss cheez ki taraf se ghaflat mein parre hue thay, balkay hum khata car thay """
  21,98,"be shak tum aur tumahray woh mabood jinhein tum pujte ho, Jahannum ka eendhan hain, wahein tum ko jana hai"
  21,99,"agar yeh waqai khuda hotay to wahan nah jatay ab sab ko hamesha isi mein rehna hai """
  21,100,wahan woh phunkaraymarain ge aur haal yeh ho ga ke is mein kaan pari aawaz nah sunai day gi
  21,101,"rahay woh log jin ke liye hamari taraf se Bhlai ka pehlay hi faisla ho chuka hoga, to woh yaqeenan uss se door rakhay jayen ge"
  21,102,is ki sarsarahat taq nah sُnin ge aur woh hamesha hamesha apni mann bhaatii cheezon ke darmain rahen ge
  21,103,"woh intahi ghabrahat ka waqt unn ko zara pareshan nah kere ga, aur mulaika barh kar unn ko hathon haath len ge ke"" yeh tumhara wohi din hai jis ka tum se wada kya jata tha """
  21,104,"woh din jabkay aasman ko hum yun lapait kar rakh den ge jaisay tomaar mein ourak lapait diye jatay hain jis terhan pehlay hum ne takhleeq ki ibtida ki thi usi terhan hum phir uss ka iada karen ge yeh aik wada hai hamaray zimmay, aur yeh kaam hamein behar haal karna hai"
  21,105,aur zaboor mein hum nasiyaat ke baad yeh likh chuke hain ke zameen ke waris hamaray naik bande hon ge
  21,106,iss mein aik barri khabar hai ibadat guzaar logon ke liye
  21,107,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum ne jo tum ko bheja hai to yeh darasal duniya walon ke haq mein hamari rehmat hai"
  21,108,"inn se kaho"" mere paas jo wahi aati hai woh yeh hai ke tumhara khuda sirf aik khuda hai, phir kya tum sar-e itaat jhukate ho? """
  21,109,"agar woh mun phairen to keh do ke"" mein ne Ali al-elaan tum ko khabardaar kar diya hai ab yeh mein nahi jaanta ke woh cheez jis ka tum se wada kya ja raha hai qareeb hai ya door"
  21,110,Allah woh baatein bhi jaanta hai jo ba aawaz buland kahi jati hain aur woh bhi jo tum chhupa kar karte ho
  21,111,"mein to yeh samjhta hon ke shayad yeh ( der ) tumahray liye aik fitnah hai aur tumhe aik waqt khaas taq ke liye mazay karne ka mauqa diya ja raha hai """
  21,112,"( aakhir kaar ) Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ne kaha ke"" ae mere rab, haq ke sath faisla kar day, aur logo, tum jo baatein banatay ho unn ke muqablay mein hamara Rab Rehman hi hamaray liye madad ka sahara hai """
